  "title": "Mustardy Mild French Sterbottensost Quiche",
  "description": "A mild and crumbly French quiche featuring Sterbottensost cheese and a mirepoix base, perfect for a kid-friendly meal. This quiche is high in protein and can be served for breakfast, lunch, or dinner.",
